About this item [Powerful Beast] - AC200MAX power station comes with amazing 2048Wh LFP cells and a 2200W inverter, making it a safe and reliable power center on the way or off-the-grid.
[Efficient, Versatile] - The hard-wearing 200-watt solar panel performs better than the market average even in low-light conditions or with shading on it.
[Super Fast Charging] - AC200MAX supports dual charging , which takes up to 900W solar and 500W AC input. Recharged by 3 PV200 solar panels, you can feed it up in less than 5 hours.
